snippet.title: Your Morning Guru with SAVY WRITES BOOKS & RK GOLD
snippet.description:
Your morning talk show diving into the world of self help and wellness hosted by Savy and RK

Your Morning Guru sparks a dialogue around the lessons and actions of popular internet creators and weigh their positive and negative consequences on those who follow them. Each week we find one positive takeaway for our show because it’s important to remember you can learn from anyone, including those you oppose

Twitter: https://twitter.com/YourMorningGuru

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/yourmorningguru/
